Company Profile




We Make Process Equipment
Growing, depositing, etching and processing thin films is our core competency.



Our Technology
Makes a Difference
Cutting-edge systems and components support energy efficiency, consumer electronics and network storage applications.



High Growth Market Focus
Our process equipment enables the manufacture of LEDs, Power Electronics, Hard Drives, MEMS, Wireless Chips and Optical System Components.



We are the Market Leader
Our technology leadership includes MOCVD, MBE, Ion Beam, Wet Etch single wafer processing and Advanced Film Process technologies.



Our R&D is Best-in-Class
Veeco’s exceptional R&D organization delivers systems that enable the future of essential technologies across the world.



