Veeco Instruments Inc.

Terminal Drive 
Plainview NY 11803 United States
Phone: +1 516-___-____
Fax: +1 516-___-____
http://www.veeco.com





19
Managers




25
IT employees




$5.9MEST.
IT Budget




Veeco is a provider of solutions for process equipment technology. This includes LED, solar, and data storage process equipment.
Veeco Instruments Inc. dedicates a sizable portion of its employees to client-side services in process technology and data storage. Subsequently, it can be difficult to find staff members focused solely on internal IT. The internal IT department mainly works in… MoreVeeco Instruments Inc. dedicates a sizable portion of its employees to client-side services in process technology and data storage. Subsequently, it can be difficult to find staff members focused solely on internal IT. The internal IT department mainly works in the areas of network infrastructure and enterprise applications.

IT business processes are seen as a key-area for increasing productivity and efficiency at Veeco. The maintenance and deployment of various SAP resources is a priority task for the IT professionals on-site.

The security of the company network is another priority for the company. A Senior Director sets protocol for risk and compliance while another IT professional carries out operations related to network security.

IT Intelligence Snippets

2013:
• Between 30-50% of IT staff is dedicated to the sustenance of its ERP platform, and less than 30% of ERP support is outsourced to a third party. 
• Expects around 4 releases/updates a year with its current ERP solution. 
• The budget is typically finalized in Q4. 
• Veeco Instruments Inc. employees 40 IT staff throughout the company.





