			Company Description 


			Veeco Instruments, Inc. designs, manufactures and markets equipment for light emitting diodes and hard disk drives, as well as concentrator photovoltaics, power semiconductors, wireless components and micro-electromechanical systems. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Plainview,...
		


                Veeco Instruments, Inc. designs, manufactures and markets equipment for light emitting diodes and hard disk drives, as well as concentrator photovoltaics, power semiconductors, wireless components and micro-electromechanical systems. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Plainview, NY.
            




